    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You twirl blades around your body at high speed, hitting all enemies around you. Target all enemies in the radius of your lowest range weapon. They must make a Dexterity saving throw or take 6d6 damage of one of your Floating Array's damage types, or half as much on a success.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, and increase the damage by 2d6.</p>",
